{"tid":2517161,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"林作公審港大生Chester Lo","createTime":"2021-05-05T07:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T07:27:20.000Z","uid":76657,"like":14,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"86be97c517be736a8f21ceba5341ee6d6a02dc97","tid":2517161,"uid":76657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:02:54.000Z","msg":"君子報仇<br />\n<br />\nChester Lo, 香港大學學生。於幾個月前加入本人團隊，但態度飄忽，訓練參與度低，在考完試後突然表示家人反對而不加入（見第二幅截圖，2月）我無所謂，但幾個禮拜後你又表示經過考慮，要我重新給一個機會給你（見第三幅圖，3月）。我給了你一個機會，你竟然在最近幾個禮拜失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n我可以接受弱者，但我一早就跟每一位recruit說過，我幾乎唯一要求，就是要溝通，要應機，要有交帶。<br />\n<br />\n而你竟敢不回覆我及我秘書的messages。<br />\n<br />\n我現在公開呼籲：此人是垃圾，為社會必須唾棄的危害份子。無論你從事任何事業，都只會是個不負責任的PK。<br />\n<br />\n我現在號召認識此人的人，無論是他的港大同學或中小學同學，與我聯絡，向我爆他的黑史，我會在此公開。<br />\n<br />\n你得罪我，我就加倍奉還。這是你的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n我希望你的父母以你為恥，我也認為你的父母沒有教好你。<br />\n<br />\n致所有保險業及將來想加入保險業的人：我來這行就是要改變風氣。我沒有看到什麼人有我如此的覺悟。我不會給任何廢人加入我的行業，而我的使命就是好好改革這行。這行裡面這種人很多，至少我在這裡堵住了一個。<br />\n<br />\n也在此警告所有加入我的人：非誠勿擾。我在訓練的是最強的團隊，你基礎不好不要緊，但你態度不好，我就給你一個人生教訓。<br />\n<br />\n這只是我的第一步。即使你爸爸媽媽來找我都會繼續。我希望你身邊所有的人都恥笑你。<br />\n<br />\n回港大校園，我要走過你的人談論你。<br />\n<br />\nWhat a loser.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTXJer7rPxYdzHrKAag92aWuRSJogtJePAjwjCqWpScRz?filename=S98d2oD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS98d2oD.png&h=4386c060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f944e62447134eace71a48908703ad8c73914387","tid":2517161,"uid":76657,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:06:53.000Z","msg":"有冇人識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf780e12178a2ca5545420bc6315d3de62c3c4f2","tid":2517161,"uid":366655,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:07:21.000Z","msg":"兩個都係垃圾<br />\n不用分得那麼細<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be09eb5fd7e08837cd7368370ce0c1ce887bc90c","tid":2517161,"uid":226231,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:08:14.000Z","msg":"條友抵死啦一啲交帶都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4eb573240d257535872611a07e0b197e10fe5b","tid":2517161,"uid":301050,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:08:31.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">你得罪我，我就加倍奉還。這是你的選擇。</span><br />\n<span class=\"red\">致所有保險業及將來想加入保險業的人：我來這行就是要改變風氣。</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />保險復仇風氣"},{"pid":"9cb6d6a66c403611562013db50ac5de2f9ab9778","tid":2517161,"uid":16777,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:08:45.000Z","msg":"cls 黑社會踢人入會咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f7f4147c0fb6f8d5d427c48809326ab24ed3e2","tid":2517161,"uid":76657,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"be09eb5fd7e08837cd7368370ce0c1ce887bc90c","tid":2517161,"uid":226231,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:08:14.000Z","msg":"條友抵死啦一啲交帶都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:09:57.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f979ae1807a0c3e54253b63c21c6c2775a6d8b3","tid":2517161,"uid":8717,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"9cb6d6a66c403611562013db50ac5de2f9ab9778","tid":2517161,"uid":16777,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:08:45.000Z","msg":"cls 黑社會踢人入會咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:10:12.000Z","msg":"一單還一單